Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:23.70,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5} Se um vidente disesse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:27.03,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}que nossa compatibilidade
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:30.29,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5} não é lá essas coisas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.29,0:22:33.83,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}ele seria um impostor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.83,0:22:37.34,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Não, não pode, não se deixe enganar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:41.30,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Quem decide o destino sou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:43.13,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Isso mesmo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:48.10,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}este é o amor verdadeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:53.94,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}É o tipo de coisa que, após morrermos
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:22:58.32,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}será exibida em um museu de arte.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:04.78,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Por isso, me deixe sempre em primeiro lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:08.37,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Me ame com todo carinho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:14.50,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}até que estas mãos que seguramos se fundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:18.38,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Vamos ficar sempre nessa vibe boa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:21.80,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Se formos nós dois, será moleza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:28.01,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Fique ao meu lado, mesmo que estejamos "chapados" de amor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:30.85,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Por favor.
